<paragraph base="SL21340363" id="IFRS10_B85L"><paranum>B85L</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 10"/><data name="paranum" value="B85L"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS10_P0532">In order to meet the requirement in <xref base="F24730538" href="IFRS10_B85K.dita#IFRS10_B85K" id="IFRS10_X0548">B85K(a)</xref>, an investment entity would:</p><ol base="SL21340364" id="IFRS10_L0045" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p base="SL21340366" id="IFRS10_P0533">elect to account for any investment property using the fair value model in <xref base="F24730539" href="../ias40/IAS40_TOC0001.dita#IAS40_TOC0001" id="IFRS10_X0549">IAS 40 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Investment Property</ph></ph></xref>;</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p base="SL21340369" id="IFRS10_P0534">elect the exemption from applying the equity method in <xref base="F24730540" href="../ias28/IAS28_TOC.dita#IAS28_TOC0001" id="IFRS10_X0550">IAS 28</xref> for its investments in associates and joint ventures; and</p></li><li><li_value>(c)</li_value> <p base="SL21340371" id="IFRS10_P0535">measure its financial assets at fair value using the requirements in <xref base="F68031688" href="../ifrs09/IFRS09_TOC.dita#IFRS09_TOC0001" id="IFRS10_X0551">IFRS 9</xref>.</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>